summary: I am a writer, a junior researcher, and a media professional. I have work experience in both the governmental and non-governmental sectors. I have a special interest in feminism, immigration, and Middle Eastern-related issues. I am the author of three published books and various published articles in Arabic newspapers and periodicals.
